---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy — Vici Sensei"
  description="What cookies (and similar technologies) Vici Sensei website uses, and what we may use in the future."
>
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="header-center">
        <span class="badge">LEGAL</span>
        <h1 class="main-title">Cookie Policy</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">What cookies and similar technologies this website uses today, and what we may introduce in the future.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: July 20, 2026</p>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <h2>1. Current Use</h2>
        <p>This website does not currently use analytics, marketing, or tracking cookies. The only technical storage in use is a small preference marker saved in your browser's local storage (not a traditional cookie) that remembers you have dismissed the cookie notice, so it does not need to reappear on every visit. This marker is strictly functional, does not identify you personally, and is not shared with any third party.</p>

        <h2>2. Cookies We May Use in the Future</h2>
        <p>As the website and mentorship program evolve, we may introduce one or more of the following categories of cookies. If we do, we will update this Policy and, where required by law, request your consent before placing any non-essential cookies.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Strictly necessary cookies</strong> — required for core functionality, such as remembering your cookie preference or keeping you signed in to the vocab app. These do not require consent under Romanian and EU law.</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> — such as Google Analytics, used to understand how visitors use the site (pages viewed, traffic sources) so we can improve it. These would require your consent.</li>
          <li><strong>Marketing cookies</strong> — such as a Meta (Facebook/Instagram) Pixel or Google Ads tag, used to measure the effectiveness of ads and show relevant offers. These would require your consent.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. How Consent Would Work</h2>
        <p>If any of the cookies above are introduced, the floating cookie icon on this website will let you accept or decline them before they are set. Declining will prevent non-essential cookies from being placed on your device. You will always be able to change your choice by clearing your browser's local storage for this site and revisiting.</p>

        <h2>4. Managing Cookies In Your Browser</h2>
        <p>Most browsers let you block or delete cookies and local storage through their settings. Doing so may affect how some websites, including parts of ours, function.</p>

        <h2>5. More Information</h2>
        <p>For details on how we handle personal data more broadly, see our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>. If you have any questions about this Cookie Policy, contact us at <span class="text-red-300">vici.sensei@gmail.com</span>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
